h-0.5 bg-navy transition-all \" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"block w-6 h-0.5 bg-navy transition-all \" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></button></nav><div id=\"mobile-menu\" class=\"md:hidden overflow-hidden transition-[max-height] duration-300 ease-out border-t border-navy/10 max-h-0\"><ul class=\"flex flex-col py-2 px-6 bg-cream\"><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/about\">About</a></li><li class=\"border-b border-navy/5\"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer\"><span>Services</span><svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 \"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"></polyline></svg></button><div class=\"overflow-hidden transition-[max-height] duration-300 ease-out max-h-0\"><ul class=\"pb-3 pl-3 border-l-2 border-orange/30 ml-1\"><li><a class=\"block py-2.5 px-3 font-exo font-semibold text-[0.8rem] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-navy/75 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/services/it-support\">IT Support &amp; Security</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-2.5 px-3 font-exo font-semibold text-[0.8rem] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-navy/75 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/services/web-design\">Web Design &amp; Hosting</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-2.5 px-3 font-exo font-semibold text-[0.8rem] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-navy/75 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/services/marketing\">Online Marketing</a></li></ul></div></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/pricing\">Pricing</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/scorecard\">Scorecard</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></li><li class=\"py-4\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary w-full justify-center\" href=\"/contact\">Get Started <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a></li></ul></div></header><main class=\"font-rajdhani\"><section class=\"bg-cream overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_1fr] gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center\"><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><p class=\"eyebrow mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>IT Support &amp; Security for Small Business</p><h1 class=\"h-section text-navy mb-7 break-words\">Reliable IT support for businesses that<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-outlined-navy\">can&#x27;t afford</span> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">downtime.</span></h1><div class=\"lg:hidden flex justify-center mb-8\"><img alt=\"Archie providing tech support\" width=\"620\" height=\"626\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full max-w-[280px] sm:max-w-[340px] h-auto object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Tech-Support.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Tech-Support.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Tech-Support.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/></div><p class=\"body-text lg:max-w-[520px] mb-9 text-[1.05rem]\">When your systems break, your email stops, or a security threat slips through — the damage doesn&#x27;t wait. We provide proactive, hands-on IT support and security built for small, local businesses. Calm support. Real people. Small business pricing.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap gap-3\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary  justify-center sm:justify-start\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to a Real Person<!-- --> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a><a class=\"btn btn-secondary  justify-center sm:justify-start\" href=\"#what-we-do\">See How We Help<!-- --> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a></div></div><div class=\"hidden lg:flex justify-end\"><img alt=\"Archie providing tech support\" width=\"620\" height=\"626\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full max-w-[400px] xl:max-w-[440px] h-auto object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Tech-Support.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Tech-Support.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Tech-Support.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_1fr] gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start\"><div><p class=\"eyebrow mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>We know the pressure</p><h2 class=\"h-section text-navy mb-7\">When you&#x27;re running lean,<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">every disruption</span> <span class=\"italic text-navy\">hits harder.</span></h2><p class=\"body-text\">There&#x27;s no IT department down the hall. When your email goes down, your systems lag, or a security issue surfaces, you&#x27;re the one dealing with it — on top of everything else. You need someone in your corner who&#x27;s already paying attention.</p></div><div class=\"bg-cream rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 p-6 lg:p-7\"><p class=\"font-exo font-extrabold text-orange text-xs tracking-[0.22em] uppercase mb-4\">Sound familiar?</p><ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-3.5\"><li class=\"flex gap-3 items-start font-exo font-medium text-navy/80 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.55]\"><span class=\"text-orange flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"8\" height=\"8\" viewBox=\"0 0 8 8\" fill=\"currentColor\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></span>Email goes down at the worst possible time</li><li class=\"flex gap-3 items-start font-exo font-medium text-navy/80 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.55]\"><span class=\"text-orange flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"8\" height=\"8\" viewBox=\"0 0 8 8\" fill=\"currentColor\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></span>Systems crawl when you need them most</li><li class=\"flex gap-3 items-start font-exo font-medium text-navy/80 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.55]\"><span class=\"text-orange flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"8\" height=\"8\" viewBox=\"0 0 8 8\" fill=\"currentColor\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></span>Phishing attempts slip past your inbox</li><li class=\"flex gap-3 items-start font-exo font-medium text-navy/80 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.55]\"><span class=\"text-orange flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"8\" height=\"8\" viewBox=\"0 0 8 8\" fill=\"currentColor\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></span>Updates and patches you never had time to run</li><li class=\"flex gap-3 items-start font-exo font-medium text-navy/80 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.55]\"><span class=\"text-orange flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"8\" height=\"8\" viewBox=\"0 0 8 8\" fill=\"currentColor\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></span>No one to call when things actually break</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-teal-gradient overflow-hidden relative\"><div class=\"hidden md:block absolute -right-8 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-orange/15 font-eurostile leading-none select-none pointer-events-none\" style=\"font-size:clamp(10rem, 22vw, 22rem)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">*</div><div class=\"section-container py-16 lg:py-24 relative z-10\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-8 md:gap-12 items-center max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\"><p class=\"font-eurostile text-orange leading-none select-none\" style=\"font-size:clamp(5rem, 10vw, 8rem)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">=</p><div><p class=\"eyebrow eyebrow-dark mb-4\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>Equal protection, fair price</p><p class=\"h-section\"><span class=\"text-white\">Small businesses deserve the<!-- --> </span><span class=\"italic text-white\">same protection</span> <span class=\"text-white\">as large ones — at a<!-- --> </span><span class=\"italic text-orange\">price that makes sense.</span></p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"what-we-do\" class=\"bg-cream scroll-mt-20 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1.2fr] gap-12 lg:gap-16 lg:items-center\"><div><p class=\"eyebrow mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>What we do</p><h2 class=\"h-section text-navy mb-7\">Straightforward IT support that keeps your business<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">protected</span> <span class=\"italic text-navy\">and running.</span></h2><p class=\"body-text mb-6\">We monitor your systems so problems get caught early. We handle issues when they come up — so you&#x27;re not left waiting on a callback from someone who doesn&#x27;t know your setup. And we protect your business against the threats that target small businesses every day.</p><p class=\"font-exo font-bold text-navy text-[1rem] leading-[1.65] max-w-[480px]\">No ticketing systems that go nowhere. No call centers that don&#x27;t know your name. Just direct support from a team that treats your business like it matters.</p></div><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 p-6 flex flex-col gap-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-orange/10 text-orange flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.2rem] lg:text-[1.3rem] tracking-wide mb-2 leading-tight\">Monitoring &amp; Alerts</h3><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/70 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.65]\">We watch your systems around the clock, staying alert so disruptions don&#x27;t catch you off guard.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 p-6 flex flex-col gap-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-orange/10 text-orange flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z\"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.2rem] lg:text-[1.3rem] tracking-wide mb-2 leading-tight\">Support When Things Break</h3><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/70 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.65]\">Fast, clear help from people who know your business — not a call center reading from a script.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 p-6 flex flex-col gap-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-orange/10 text-orange flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.2rem] lg:text-[1.3rem] tracking-wide mb-2 leading-tight\">Security Protection</h3><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/70 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.65]\">Threat detection, safe email practices, and layered defenses sized for your business and budget.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 p-6 flex flex-col gap-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-orange/10 text-orange flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><polyline points=\"23 4 23 10 17 10\"></polyline><polyline points=\"1 20 1 14 7 14\"></polyline><path d=\"M3.51 9a9 9 0 0 1 14.85-3.36L23 10M1 14l4.64 4.36A9 9 0 0 0 20.49 15\"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.2rem] lg:text-[1.3rem] tracking-wide mb-2 leading-tight\">Ongoing Maintenance</h3><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/70 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.65]\">Updates, patches, and regular checkups that keep things running smoothly between calls.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between gap-4 mb-10\"><div><p class=\"eyebrow mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>What&#x27;s included</p><h2 class=\"h-compact text-navy\">Everything a<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">small business</span> <!-- -->IT department would do —<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-navy\">without the overhead.</span></h2></div><a class=\"font-exo font-